{"tid":1337484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住 我無圖 但都要分享情報","createTime":"2019-07-21T09:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T09:54:04.000Z","uid":258663,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e061ed075b1fc528560ff1827f123b6ca2c103f","tid":1337484,"uid":258663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:36:40.000Z","msg":"因同行有人唔舒服  要陪佢先走 <br />\n去坐隧巴 係稅務大樓附近 有圍數唔少嘅白衫人 唔係犬<br />\n有啲有紋身 有啲裡面著件衫再著多件白衫係面 佢見我同友人全黑 睥到實 <br />\n但係我唔敢影佢地相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住聽到有九巴職員話可能就封路 現場告士打道<br />\n叫我地過海就求其上左架車先<br />\n最後走左<br />\n<br />\n我只係想講現場人愈多佢地愈唔敢亂黎 不過今日似乎唔係得犬要應付<br />\n<br />\nBe Water.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1700f5746084c05c0ad0e991021bd8c79c6bdcf4","tid":1337484,"uid":258663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:39:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c9735ff1c2789cd8a9ed9b57e1a3f6bb53bdfa35","tid":1337484,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:39:21.000Z","msg":"網上軍師，<br />\n現場決定，<br />\n相信現場"},{"pid":"68c815df058691732ff8f079afbcc14244b34639","tid":1337484,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:40:15.000Z","msg":"我都見到"},{"pid":"55fc07c53b4710f59ff2521981f7aedda3e36e9c","tid":1337484,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:40:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5519125855d983a500f43c3bfca67bce647995b9","tid":1337484,"uid":46534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74de8d9498d8fc0d3a6bb6ffabd38f2ddb858486","tid":1337484,"uid":46534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T09:44:33.000Z","msg":"遠遠地影，佢地好似成班等緊啲野咁<br />\n人數唔多，有少少惡意"},{"pid":"303bc9739d11493c77934b5b9f3b944741ffe7a2","tid":1337484,"uid":258663,"like":0,"